results.name: Number of unlabeled free bicolored trees with n nodes (the colors are not interchangeable).
reference: R. W. Robinson, Numerical implementation of graph counting algorithms, AGRC Grant, Math. Dept., Univ. Newcastle, Australia, 1978.
link: Andrew Howroyd, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..500
formula: G.f.: 2*f(x) - f(x)^2 where f(x) is the g.f. of A000081. - _Andrew Howroyd_, Nov 02 2019
program: (PARI) \\ here TreeGf is A000081 as g.f.
TreeGf(N)={my(A=vector(N, j, 1)); for (n=1, N-1, A[n+1] = 1/n * sum(k=1, n, sumdiv(k, d, d*A[d]) * A[n-k+1] ) ); x*Ser(A)}
xref: Same as A125702 except for n = 1.
